    <h2>
        BordaCount on LETOR4.0</h2>
    
    <p>
        BordaCount is a popular aggregation method which simply computes the ranking score
        of an object based on the number of objects that are ranked below it in all the
        ranking lists. Details can be found at <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Borda_count">
            wiki</a>.</p>
